\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch
  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(2) The sovereignty of the working people, realized on the basis of democratic centralism, is the fundamental principle of the structure of the state.}
