  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(1) The People's Chamber determines the goals of the development of the German Democratic Republic in a final and binding manner for everyone by means of laws and resolutions.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch
  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(2) The People's Chamber sets the main rules for the interaction of citizens, communities and state organs as well as their tasks in the implementation of state plans for social development.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch
  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(3) The People's Chamber guarantees the implementation of its laws and resolutions. It determines the principles of the operation of the Council of State, the Council of Ministers, the National Defense Council, the Supreme Court and the Attorney General.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049\rtlch \ltrch\loch

